Thanx for reading!
By

I waited all day to meet my friends friend, and right at the last moment she cancelled cause she's a little biatch.  Just kidding.  

Now I want to eat, even though I'm not hungry.  Whenever I'm depressed I eat.  It sucks.  Now I'm in my pajamas lounging around doing CRAP.  And I just realize that everyone, even people who aren't religious have crosses in their houses.  And a lot of people who aren't, don't.  Weird.  

My lips are so freaking chapped.  But I had a little facial, and it was very relaxing...or whatever.  Now I don't know what to do.  I think my friend's mom should take us to the store and get us each a pint of ice cream....

I'm bored.  I'm gonna shoot myself.  Just kidding.  Again.  But I am gonna shoot all the preppy 8th graders.  And the little short kid named Dakota....He stalks me.  I swear. 

Anyways, I have to go.  Thanks for reading...homie Gs....or whatever you gangstas say.  Bye
